      "snowpackStructure": {
        "comment": "15 to 30 cm of snow has fallen since Sunday. 15 to 20 cm of snow, and even more in some localities, will fall until Wednesday. The wind will be strong to storm force. <br/> <br/> The fresh snow and in particular the extensive wind slabs will be deposited on a weakly bonded old snowpack in particular on west, north and east facing slopes above the tree line. <br/> In some places various wind slab layers are lying on surface hoar. <br/> Faceted weak layers exist in the bottom section of the snowpack."
      },
